 conf-sanity test_43a: @@@@@@ FAIL: check lustre-MDTall.mdt.nosquash_nids failed!
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;00000020:00000400:6.0:1720555881.856466:0:351984:0:(lprocfs_status.c:2381:lprocfs_wr_nosquash_nids()) lustre-MDT0000: failed to set nosquash_nids to &quot;2@gni 0@lo 2601:8c1:c180:2000::cbdc@tcp 192.168.0.[2,10]@tcp&quot;, can&apos;t parse rc = -22
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
