                            <comment id="460535" author="adilger" created="Thu, 19 Jun 2025 12:01:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like this is an interop test bug introduced by patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/55922&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/55922&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14288&quot; title=&quot;Enhance nodemap ranges to work better with IPv6&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-14288&quot;&gt;LU-14288&lt;/a&gt; lnet: Introduce nidmasks&quot;) because old MDS versions do not support nidmasks. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It first appeared on master-next on 2024-11-12 and then on master on 2024-11-24 after patch 55922 landed, and has been failing ever since then. &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/search?status%5B%5D=FAIL&amp;amp;test_set_script_id=7f66aa20-3db2-11e0-80c0-52540025f9af&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=0bcdb25a-8314-11e5-b9d3-5254006e85c2&amp;amp;start_date=2024-09-01&amp;amp;end_date=2025-01-01&amp;amp;source=sub_tests#redirect&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/search?status%5B%5D=FAIL&amp;amp;test_set_script_id=7f66aa20-3db2-11e0-80c0-52540025f9af&amp;amp;sub_test_script_id=0bcdb25a-8314-11e5-b9d3-5254006e85c2&amp;amp;start_date=2024-09-01&amp;amp;end_date=2025-01-01&amp;amp;source=sub_tests#redirect&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

